ains less than 2,000 records, try resetting the limit.","Try simplifying the formula.","Try moving your data to a different data source."],"whyFix":"","level":"Medium","componentType":"app","primaryCategory":"formula"}},{"id":"app-SuggestRemoteExecutionHint-InOpRhs","messageStrings":{"issue":{"text":"Delegation warning. The highlighted part of this formula might not work correctly on large data sets."}},"properties":{"howToFix":["Change the item to the right of the \"in\" operator to be a column from the correct data source.","If your data set exceeds the 500 record limit but contains less than 2,000 records, try resetting the limit.","Try simplifying the formula.","Try moving your data to a different data source."],"whyFix":"","level":"Medium","componentType":"app","primaryCategory":"formula"}},{"id":"app-SuggestRemoteExecutionHint-OpNotSupportedByColumn","messageStrings":{"issue":{"text":"Delegation warning. The highlighted part of this formula might not work correctly with column \"{0}\" on large data sets."}},"properties":{"howToFix":["If your data set exceeds the 500 record limit but contains less than 2,000 records, try resetting the limit.","Try simplifying the formula.","Try moving your data to a different data source."],"whyFix":"","level":"Medium","componentType":"app","primaryCategory":"formula"}},{"id":"acc-AccessibleLabelNeeded","messageStrings":{"issue":{"text":"Missing accessible label"}},"properties":{"howToFix":["Edit the accessible label property to describe the item."],"whyFix":"If there's no accessible text, people who can’t see the screen won't understand what’s in images and controls.","level":"Medium","componentType":"app","primaryCategory":"accessibility"}},{"id":"acc-TabIndexShouldBeDefinedForInteractiveControl","messageStrings":{"issue":{"text":"Missing tab stop"}},"properties":{"howToFix":["Set TabIndex to 0 or greater to ensure that interactive elements have a tab stop."],"whyFix":"People who use the keyboard with your app will not be able to access this element without a tab stop.","level":"Medium","componentType":"app","primaryCategory":"accessibility"}},{"id":"acc-FocusBorderShouldBeVisible","messageStrings":{"issue":{"text":"Focus isn't showing"}},"properties":{"howToFix":["Change the FocusedBorderThickness property to be more than 0."],"whyFix":"If the focus isn't visible, people who don't use a mouse won't be able to see it when they're interacting with the app.","level":"Medium","componentType":"app","primaryCategory":"accessibility"}},{"id":"app-UnusedVariables","messageStrings":{"issue":{"text":"Unused variable"}},"properties":{"howToFix":["Remove the unused variable."],"whyFix":"This variable is declared but is not referenced by any control, so it is not needed.","componentType":"app","primaryCategory":"performance","level":"Medium"}},{"id":"app-CollectDelegatableDataSource","messageStrings":{"issue":{"text":"The rows retrieved from the data source may not be complete."}},"properties":{"howToFix":["Limit the data collected from the data source by updating the formula \"ClearCollect(colAllPayments, Payments)\" to include a filtering function, such as 'Filter' or 'Search'."],"whyFix":"Using the 'Collect' function to create a collection directly from a connected data source may not load every row if the data source is too large.","componentType":"app","primaryCategory":"performance","level":"Medium"}},{"id":"app-DataSourceDefaultMaxRowsLimit","messageStrings":{"issue":{"text":"Data row limit for non-delegable queries is more than 500"}},"properties":{"howToFix":["Update 'Data row limit for non-delegable queries' in the advanced app settings."],"whyFix":"A 'data row limit' more than 500 may result in a slower app when running non-delegable queries, because the app will have to process every row itself, rather than running the query on the server.","componentType":"app","primaryCategory":"performance","level":"Medium"}},{"id":"app-ScreenHasManyControls","messageStrings":{"issue":{"text":"Too many controls on a screen"}},"properties":{"howToFix":["Reduce the number of controls on the screen.","Break the app into more screens to reduce the per-screen complexity.","Use components to unify grouped controls that are identical across screens, reducing duplication.","Use galleries to represent a series of repeated similar controls.","Break the app into multiple apps so that each app is small and performant."],"whyFix":"Each control consumes resources, and an app may become slow or unresponsive if a screen has too many controls. The estimated complexity of \"scrDashboard\" is 633, which exceeds the maximum threshold recommended (300).","componentType":"app","primaryCategory":"performance","level":"Medium"}},{"id":"app-NumericPropertySizeWarning","messageStrings":{"issue":{"text":"Allowing upload of large files up to 10 MB"}},"properties":{"howToFix":["Consider whether you need attachments of this size."],"whyFix":"We recommend testing on all supported platforms to ensure that attachments of this size can be uploaded successfully.","componentType":"app","primaryCategory":"performance","level":"Low"}}]}},"invocations":[{"executionSuccessful":true}],"columnKind":"utf16CodeUnits"}]}